{
  "stem": "19055.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Every time I would breathe, I felt stabbing on both sides and I could hardly breathe.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was short of breath.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was weak.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I couldn't practically stand up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was lying down in the-- in the boxcar, my parents, my sister around me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And nobody knows what, why, and there was no-- no help, no cure.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Another day passed, and it was going on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The train was moving again in a slow pace and faster pace.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And maybe the third or fourth day [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] before that I celebrated my birthday.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The 10th of April, 1945, I became 15.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] [SIGHS] To me, the celebration was to-- to get a deep breath and get enough oxygen.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So on-- Another day passed, and another day passed, and the train, each time, was going slower and slower.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we began to hear some unusual noises like woo-woo, distant cannon or distant thunders.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "What-- I really didn't know what they were.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But they were battlefield noises, probably cannons, or tank cannons, or bombings.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We didn't know what it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But these noises became stronger and stronger, and were getting closer to us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So on the day of April the 13th, the plane stopped--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not the plane, the train.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The train stopped and the engine decoupled.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The engineers took off with the engine.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They left the train, without an engine, standing there, the middle of the-- the rails in a forest.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Actually, next to a forest.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we're standing there and standing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And somebody looked outside through the barbed wired window and saw that SS was tearing off their insignia.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were tearing off the skull and bones, and the SS, and some of them were changing-- changing to civilian uniforms.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
